high_descs: Walk around the table to face the opposite side.
Pick up the box of tissues on the table.
Turn right and walk forward to face the night stand to the left of the bed.
Place the box of tissues on the left side of the lamp.
Turn around and walk around the table to the right to face the right side.
Pick up the box of tissues on the table.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the night stand.
Place the tissue box on the right side of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: To put two tissue boxes on the night stand.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the chair, then hang a right and walk around to the far side of the wooden table.
Pick up the closest tissue box off of the wooden table.
Turn right and walk up to the small black table to the left of the bed.
Put the tissue box on the small black table to the left of the lamp.
Turn left and walk towards the chair, then hang a left and walk over to the wooden table.
Pick up the tissue box off of the wooden table.
Turn left and walk over to the small black table next to the bed with the lamp on it.
Put the tissue box on the small black table to the left of the tissue box that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two tissue boxes to a small black table.
